6月1日，[[古巴|古巴]]以西近海有结构严密的云系发展成热带低气压。系统缓慢向东北方向穿越[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]，于6月3日增强成热带风暴并获名“阿尔伯托”（{{lang|en|Alberto}}）。风暴的移动方向很不稳定，但总体是朝东北前进，然后短暂达到一级飓风标准，成为有纪录以来在形成日期最早的6月飓风之一，也是1970年5月的[[1970年飓风阿尔玛|飓风阿尔玛]]过后形成日期最早的大西洋飓风。<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-021716.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-02-17 | accessdate = 2016-05-11 | location = Miami, FL | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160411090349/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-021716.txt | archivedate = 2016-04-11 }}</ref>接下来由于[[风切变|垂直风切变]]逐渐增多，气旋迅速减弱成热带风暴，然后回转向西，于6月6日在[[佛罗里达礁岛群|佛罗里达礁岛群]]附近完全消散。进入墨西哥后没有[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]便告消散的风暴很少，阿尔伯托便是其中之一。<ref name="HURDAT" />

阿尔贝托虽然自始至终均未登陆，但古巴还是因重大洪灾导致23人丧生，是该国32年来致死人数最多的洪灾。佛罗里达州南部出现中等程度降水，降雨量最高的是[[门罗县_(佛罗里达州)|门罗县]]的[[塔弗尼尔_(佛罗里达州)|塔弗尼尔]]（{{lang|en|Tavernier}}），达418毫米。<ref>{{cite report | author = David Roth | year = 2009 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064613/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/alberto1982.html | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/alberto1982.html | title = Hurricane Alberto Rainfall Totals | deadurl = no | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2016-05-11 | date =  }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | author = Miles B. Lawrence | year = 1983 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/alberto/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303212323/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/alberto/ | title = Hurricane Alberto Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-11 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>
