本季首场[[亚热带气旋|亚热带风暴]]于6月18日在墨西哥湾中东部形成，之后一直向东北方向前进直至消散。气旋于18日当晚穿过[[佛罗里达半岛|佛罗里达半岛]]，当地因此收到多份强烈[[雷暴|雷暴]]天气和[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]警告。风暴还降下暴雨，德索托市（{{lang|en|DeSoto City}}）西南方向约13公里处测得272毫米雨量，为全州最高。<ref>{{cite report | author = David M. Roth | year = 2009 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/stjun1982filledrainblk.gif | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075541/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/stjun1982filledrainblk.gif | format = GIF | title = Rainfall from Subtropical Storm One | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2016-05-11 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | date =  }}</ref>系统继续前进，经过[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]的[[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]后仍得以保持强度，直至6月20日在[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]附近转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。气旋在佛罗里达州夺走三条人命，还令北卡罗莱纳州近海的一艘[[拖网渔船|拖网渔船]]沉没，造成的损失总额约为1000万美元（1998年美元）。<ref>{{cite report | author = Joseph Pelissier | year = 1983 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/subtrop/ | title = Subtropical Storm One Report | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-11 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303191606/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/subtrop/ | date =  }}</ref>1982年大西洋飓风季只有这一场热带或亚热带风暴曾直接袭击[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]<ref name="cliqr">{{cite report | author = David M. Roth | year = 2009 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/roth/ebtrk_nhc_final.txt | title = CLIQR tropical cyclone database | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2016-05-11 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304002251/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/roth/ebtrk_nhc_final.txt | deadurl = no | format = TXT | date =  }}</ref>。
