8月27日，一股发展状况良好的[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲海岸，次日就发展成热带低气压，不久后又升级成热带风暴并获名“贝里尔”（{{lang|en|Beryl}}）。8月29日，气旋从[[佛得角|佛得角]]以南近海掠过，并在朝[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向前进期间继续强化。8月31日，对流内有[[风眼|眼状特征]]呈现，表明风速已接近飓风标准，但考虑到眼状特征的位置在深层对流西侧，风暴结构还不够对称，因此估计贝里尔的强度还是略低于飓风下限。<ref name="PRPG1">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Preliminary Report, Page One | year = 1983 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-05-11 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | location = Miami, FL | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/beryl/prelim01.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303180227/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/beryl/prelim01.gif | format = GIF | date =  }}</ref>此后不久，气旋受强烈风切变的影响而开始消退，下层环流从对流西侧逐渐暴露出来<ref name="PRPG1" />。次日，缺乏对流的贝里尔降级成热带低气压，然后继续西进，在此期间没有重新发展。9月5日，飞入系统的侦察机测得每小时100公里风速，但由于此数据是在[[飑线|飑线]]上测得，因此不能代表风暴的实际强度。气旋结构再度变得混乱，到了9月6日晚，卫星已无法继续追踪。<ref name="PRPG2">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Preliminary Report, Page Two | year = 1983 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-05-11 | format = GIF | location = Miami, FL | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/beryl/prelim02.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303231410/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/beryl/prelim02.gif | date =  }}</ref>

贝里尔存在早期就在佛得角[[萨尔岛|萨尔岛]]产生暴雨和强烈阵风，佛得角群岛普遍受到中等程度破坏，损失总额约有300万美元（1982年美元）<ref name="em-dat">{{cite web | author = EM-DAT: the International Disaster Database | year = 2007 | title = Disaster List for Cape Verde | publisher = Centre for Research on the Epidemiology of Disasters | accessdate = 2016-05-11 | url = http://www.emdat.be/ | archive-date = 2014-02-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140215235623/http://www.emdat.be/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。风暴导致[[布拉瓦岛|布拉瓦岛]]三人丧生，另有122人受伤<ref>{{cite web | author = Office of U.S. Foreign Disaster Assistance | year = 1992 | url = http://pdf.usaid.gov/pdf_docs/PNABP986.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303232922/http://pdf.usaid.gov/pdf_docs/PNABP986.pdf | title = Disaster History: Major Disasters Worldwide 1900 – present | publisher = Labat-Anderson Incorporated | accessdate = 2016-05-11 | deadurl = no | format = PDF | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}}</ref>。贝里尔过去后，美国向佛得角提供经济及人道主义援助，协助当地恢复到灾前状态<ref name="geo-iq">{{cite report | author = Geography I.Q. | year = 2007 | title = U.S.-CAPE VERDEAN RELATIONS | url = http://www.geographyiq.com/countries/cv/Cape_Verde_us_relations_summary.htm | deadurl = no | publisher = Geography I.Q. | accessdate = 2016-05-11 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303181151/http://www.geographyiq.com/countries/cv/Cape_Verde_us_relations_summary.htm | date =  }}</ref>。
