9月8日，[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]内发展出地面[[低气压|低气压区]]。系统向西飘移，于次日组织成[[亚热带气旋|亚热带低气压]]。受[[低压槽|低压槽]]影响，低气压转向北上，组织结构稳步改善，于9月10日转变成热带风暴并得名“克里斯”（{{lang|en|Chris}}）。达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]100公里的最高强度后，气旋从德克萨斯州萨宾帕斯（{{lang|en|Sabine Pass}}）附近登陆，然后继续朝内陆行进，最终于9月13日在[[阿肯色州|阿肯色州]]中部上空消散。路易斯安那州南部有6500人疏散，海上多个石油平台的工作人员也转移也内陆。<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | author = Gilbert B. Clark | date = 1982-09-27 | title = Tropical Storm Chris Prelimary Report | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/chris/prelim01.gif | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = GIF | location = Miami, FL | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303230015/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/chris/prelim01.gif }}</ref>

克里斯沿途普降中雨，并以[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]][[新德里_(路易斯安那州)|新德里]]最多，达410毫米，[[密西西比州|密西西比州]]和[[田纳西州|田纳西州]]的降雨总量都在250毫米以上<ref name="ChrisRain">{{cite report | author = David Roth | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall: Tropical Storm Chris | publisher = Hydrometeorogical Prediction Center | accessdate = 2016-05-12 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/chris1982.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304091234/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/chris1982.html | date =  }}</ref>。远至田纳西州及[[肯塔基州|肯塔基州]]这样的内陆州份都因降雨引发局部严重洪灾，还有多条河流泛滥<ref name="Significant Floods">{{cite web | author = U.S. Geological Survey Kansas Water Science Center | year = 2007 | title = Summary of Significant Floods in the United States, Puerto Rico, and the Virgin Islands, 1970 Through 1989 – 1982 | publisher = U.S. Geological Survey Kansas Water Science Center | accessdate = 2016-05-12 | url = http://ks.water.usgs.gov/pubs/reports/wsp.2502.sum82.html#HDR1 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304023118/http://ks.water.usgs.gov/pubs/reports/wsp.2502.sum82.html#HDR1 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。风暴还催生出九场龙卷风，其中有四级的强度达到[[藤田级数|藤田级数]]的{{lang|en|F}}2级以上<ref name="Torndoes">{{cite web | author = Tom Grazulis of The Tornado Project and Bill McCaul of USRA Huntsville | year = 2007 | title = List of Known Tropical Cyclones Which Have Spawned Tornadoes | publisher = Tornado Project | accessdate = 2016-05-12 | url = http://www.tornadoproject.com/alltorns/allhurricanes.htm | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304125758/http://www.tornadoproject.com/alltorns/allhurricanes.htm | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。登岸期间，气旋产生1.8米高的风暴潮，对墨西哥湾的许多船只构成严重破坏。克里斯沿途造成的损失总额约为200万美元（1982年美元）<ref name="TCR" />。
