{{main|1982年飓风黛比}}
一股[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲西岸向西移动，逐渐穿越大西洋并于9月13 日在[[海地|海地]]北岸近海组织成热带低气压。气旋转向北上，增强成热带风暴后又进一步升级为飓风。黛比向东北偏北移动，以热带风暴强度掠过百慕大。飓风北上期间继续增强，最终达到的最强风速为每小时210公里。飓风黛比在北纬38°8成为四级飓风，截至2015年仍是有纪录以来唯一在北纬38°以北达到四级飓风强度的风暴，也是位置最偏北的四级大西洋飓风之一，仅次于1978年的[[1978年飓风艾拉|飓风艾拉]]。9月18日气旋经过期间，纽芬兰岛[[开普雷斯|开普雷斯]]（{{lang|en|Cape Race}}）测得热带风暴强度大风。接下来黛比的移动速度加快，并因行经洋面水温降低而开始减弱。9月20日，风暴同[[不列颠群岛|不列颠群岛]]上空一个不具备热带特征的天气系统合并。<ref name="Dctc">{{cite report | work = National Hurricane Center | year = 1983 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/debby/ | title = Hurricane Debby Report | accessdate = 2016-05-12 | location = Miami, FL | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304000934/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/debby/ | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>

黛比的扰动天气前身令[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]普降暴雨，降雨量最高的是该岛西南部，达到327毫米<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304091357/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/debby1982.html | author = David Roth | year = 2006 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/debby1982.html | title = ncipent Stage of Debby - September 12-14, 1982 | accessdate = 2016-05-12 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | work = Weather Prediction Center | location = [[大学公园市|College Park]], [[马里兰州|Maryland]] | publisher = NOAA/ [[美国国家气象局|National Weather Service]] | date =  }}</ref><ref name="Dctc" />。除降下暴雨外，飓风对[[加拿大大西洋省份|加拿大大西洋省份]]的影响很小<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Canadian Hurricane Centre | date = 2003-09-18 | url = http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/storm82.html | title = Storms of 1982 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20060513212951/http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/storm82.html | work = The Green Lane | accessdate = 2006-05-13 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2006-05-13 }}</ref>。
